Appointment to State Court of Appeal Confirmed by Commission on Judicial
Appointments

   SacramentoChief Justice Ronald M. George, Chair of the Commission on
   Judicial Appointments, announced that the commission today confirmed
   the appointment of Judge Ronald B. Robie, of the Superior Court of
   Sacramento County, to the office of Associate Justice of the Court of
   Appeal for the Third Appellate District (Sacramento).

   The confirmation was approved by unanimous vote at a public hearing
   held in the California Supreme Court Courtroom, 110 Library and Courts
   Building, Sacramento.































